Interface UtilityFunction

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    MRubisSelfHealingUtilityFunction, MRubisSelfOptimizationUtilityFunction

    public interface UtilityFunction
    Utility function to compute the utility of the managed system. The system is described by the CompArch model whose root element is of type Architecture.
    Version:
    0.41
    Author:
    thomas vogel

      • computeUtility

        double computeUtility(Architecture architecture)
        Computes the utility of a managed system described by its Architecture.
        Parameters:
        architecture - the system for which the utility should be computed. This object is the root element of a CompArch model.
        Returns:
        the utility for the given Architecture.
